title: Canadian chargé's ambition to canoe in Bratislava
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Canada’s Chargé d’affaires John von Kaufmann has learnt a lot about Slovak history. Moreover, in Bratislava, he discovered a nudist beach and a farmers’ market by accident. How’s life in the capital going for him? 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec 
Photo: TASR
